content.comment:
All three reviewers initially recommended reject.  The main concerns were:
1) weak technical contribution and insight [R1, R2, R3, R4];
2) incremental novelty (another variation of SiamFC) [R1, R2, R3];
3) unconvincing experiment results against missing SOTA [R1, R2, R3];

The author's response did not assuage these concerns.

